(3, '2017年12月第2套', '理解他人', 'For this part, you are allowed 30 minutes to write an essay commenting on the saying "Seek to understand others, and you will be understood." You can cite examples to illustrate your views. You should write at least 150 words but no more than 200 words.', 2017, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'task1', 150, 200, 106, 'CET-6 2017年12月第2套', 1),
